    "description": "Colony X 是一款多人太空恐怖游戏。一个玩家扮演可以在任何表面行走的生物Xeon。其他玩家（2-4人）扮演殖民者，试图逃跑或猎杀Xeon。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/de524044597c792b0a0d2395900e8a0c.poster.avif?t=1767713507\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/de524044597c792b0a0d2395900e8a0c.webm?t=1767713507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/de524044597c792b0a0d2395900e8a0c.mp4?t=1767713507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>为了寻找新的殖民地，殖民者们离开了地球，但在旅途中遇到了意想不到的故障。迫切需要补给，他们在一个看似废弃的太空站寻求庇护。然而，当他们一踏入其中，事情就开始变得不对劲。安全系统启动，机库门在他们身后锁上了。现在，已经没有退路了。<br><br>殖民者们必须破解门的密码并收集必要的补给品以生存下去。但当他们穿过黑暗、寒冷的走廊时，一个问题不断萦绕在他们的脑海中：“这个太空站真的被废弃了吗？”奇怪的回声、突如其来的停电和移动的阴影暗示着，这个太空站可能不像看上去那么空旷。现在，问题不只是收集补给品，而是如何在这个神秘的地方中从未知的危险中生存下来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/673a819458f11f02c91da90fe3979efe.avif?t=1767713507\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/a59638116bdd10fe6e522a703cb6aa44.poster.avif?t=1767713507\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/a59638116bdd10fe6e522a703cb6aa44.webm?t=1767713507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/a59638116bdd10fe6e522a703cb6aa44.mp4?t=1767713507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Xeon能够在任何表面上移动。它不能打开锁住的门，但可以通过隧道进入几乎任何地方。控制Xeon提供了一种独特的游戏体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/0728f7fb11b3ce56d259df5a65d7a600.avif?t=1767713507\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/35f8d88ba4733c850ce7412485387850.poster.avif?t=1767713507\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/35f8d88ba4733c850ce7412485387850.webm?t=1767713507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/35f8d88ba4733c850ce7412485387850.mp4?t=1767713507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>如果你被Xeon抓住，它会将你孵化，变成一个新生的Xeonlet。现在你要为它而战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/e3d4f7b876bf5d09681111c78c38b899.avif?t=1767713507\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/5500f1d93eea960cb2d1e50fbc9fdb7e.poster.avif?t=1767713507\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/5500f1d93eea960cb2d1e50fbc9fdb7e.webm?t=1767713507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/5500f1d93eea960cb2d1e50fbc9fdb7e.mp4?t=1767713507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>为了逃脱Xeon，殖民者必须破解机库门的密码或进入武器库。他们需要注意天花板和隧道。危险不仅仅来自地面。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/1fb0206096292187aec5443d2a83d50e.avif?t=1767713507\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/14d635785e0ea1b729207398b9daa074.poster.avif?t=1767713507\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/14d635785e0ea1b729207398b9daa074.webm?t=1767713507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/14d635785e0ea1b729207398b9daa074.mp4?t=1767713507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>破解机库密码后，你需要穿上宇航服，准备进行太空行走。小心！如果在外门打开之前内门没有关闭，你将被抛入太空。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/bad093b28dc2f739239a4d062020c7b6.avif?t=1767713507\" width=600 height=71 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/c7fc87b2b1a78e8cd4b8394d0f150883.poster.avif?t=1767713507\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/c7fc87b2b1a78e8cd4b8394d0f150883.webm?t=1767713507\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216370/extras/c7fc87b2b1a78e8cd4b8394d0f150883.mp4?t=1767713507\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在收集到修理所需的材料后，你需要进行太空行走，返回你的主舰。",
